			"<div id = \"section_4\"><span id = \"Description\"></span><h3 class = \"editable\"> Description </h3>\n<p>The value returned by <code>getMonth</code> is an integer between 0 and 11. 0 corresponds to January, 1 to February, and so on.\n</p>\n</div>",
			"<div id = \"section_5\"><span id = \"Examples\"></span><h3 class = \"editable\"> Examples </h3>\n<div id = \"section_6\"><span id = \"Example:_Using_getMonth\"></span><h4 class = \"editable\"> Example: Using <code>getMonth</code> </h4>\n<p>The second statement below assigns the value 11 to the variable <code>month</code>, based on the value of the <code>Date</code> object <code>Xmas95</code>.\n</p>\n<pre>\nXmas95 = new Date(&quot;December 25, 1995 23:15:00&quot;)\nmonth = Xmas95.getMonth() \n</pre>\n</div></div>",
