			"<div id = \"section_1\"><span id = \"Summary\"></span><h3 class = \"editable\">Summary</h3>\n<p>Binds an object's property to a function to be called when that property is looked up.</p>\n<table class = \"standard-table\"> <thead> <tr> <th class = \"header\" colspan = \"2\">Method of <a title = \"en/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\" rel = \"internal\" href = \"https://developer.mozilla.org/en/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a></th> </tr> </thead> <tbody> <tr> <td>Implemented in</td> <td>JavaScript ?</td> </tr> <tr> <td>ECMAScript Edition</td> <td>None</td> </tr> </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>",
			"<div id = \"section_2\"><span id = \"Syntax\"></span><h3 class = \"editable\">Syntax</h3>\n<p><code><em>obj</em>.__defineGetter__(<em>sprop</em>, <em>fun</em>)</code></p>\n</div>",
			"<div id = \"section_3\"><span id = \"Parameters\"></span><h3 class = \"editable\">Parameters</h3>\n<dl> <dt><code>sprop</code></dt> <dd>a string containing the name of the property to bind to the given function</dd>\n</dl>\n<dl> <dt><code>fun</code></dt> <dd>a function to be bound to a lookup of the specified property</dd>\n</dl>\n</div>",
			"<div id = \"section_4\"><span id = \"Description\"></span><h3 class = \"editable\">Description</h3>\n<p>The <code>__defineGetter__</code> allows a <a title = \"en/Core_JavaScript_1.5_Reference/Operators/Special_Operators/get_Operator\" rel = \"internal\" href = \"https://developer.mozilla.org/en/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/Special/get\">getter</a> to be defined on a pre-existing object.</p>\n</div>",
			"<div id = \"section_5\"><span id = \"See_also\"></span><h3 class = \"editable\">See also</h3>\n<ul> <li><a title = \"en/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/Special_Operators/get_Operator\" rel = \"internal\" href = \"https://developer.mozilla.org/en/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/Special/get\">get</a></li> <li><a title = \"en/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/lookupGetter\" rel = \"internal\" href = \"https://developer.mozilla.org/en/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/lookupGetter\">__lookupGetter__</a></li> <li><a title = \"en/Core_JavaScript_1.5_Guide/Creating_New_Objects/Defining_Getters_and_Setters\" rel = \"internal\" href = \"https://developer.mozilla.org/en/JavaScript/Guide/Obsolete_Pages/Creating_New_Objects/Defining_Getters_and_Setters\">JS Guide:Defining Getters and Setters</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p></p></div>"
